  "MtPyre_Summit_EventScript_OldMan": {
    "dialogue": [
      "MT. PYRE is where we calm the spirits\nof POKéMON that have passed on…\nThis is a high place where one can\nsee all of HOENN…\nThe disembodied spirits of POKéMON\nmust find solace here…\nIs it coincidence that you are here…\nWill you hear out my tale? A tale long\ntold in the HOENN region?",
      "It is my role to pass on the legends\nof HOENN to future generations.\nAnd the crisis that just ended in\nSOOTOPOLIS rewrote a legend…\nHave you the time to hear the new\nlegend of HOENN?"
    ],
    "story": []
  },
  "MtPyre_Summit_EventScript_OldLady": {
    "dialogue": [
      "The BLUE ORB and RED ORB taken by\nthose sinister men…\nThey must never be apart…\nI fear something terrible will happen…",
      "The embodiments of the land, sea,\nand the sky…\nThat is said to be the identities of\nthe super-ancient POKéMON…\nIn the same way that we humans and\nPOKéMON have life, our world, too,\nis alive…\nThe super-ancient POKéMON have\ntaught us that…",
      "Oh, my goodness…\nYou say that both GROUDON and KYOGRE\nhave been awakened?\nIt is said that the BLUE ORB and\nthe RED ORB quelled the rage of\nthe two POKéMON…\nIt is also said that the true owner\nof the ORBS still exists.\nHowever, no one knows who, or what\nexactly, the ORBS belong to.\nIt could be a human, or perhaps\na POKéMON, but no one knows."
    ],
    "story": []
  },
